title: The New Regime - Coup
description:
El disco debut del proyecto como solista de Ilan Rubin (el chico del cabello que 

toca la bateria con Nine Inch Nails).


El proyecto se llama THE NEW REGIME  y el disco se titula COUP. Fue lanzado el 18 de 

Noviembre de 2008 a traves de los medios digitales (itunes, amazon mp3, etc) 

(esperemos pronto el producto fisico)


10 temas totalmente compuestos, tocados y grabados por el mismo Ilan Rubin, cada 

nota de Piano, Guitarra, Bajo, Bateria, viene de las manos de Ilan quien tambien 

es quien canta y hace los coros.


Calidad: MP3 @ 112kbps(se que no es la mejor calidad pero si te agrada y quieresmejor calidad, simplemente compra el album)(esperemos pronto el producto fisico en tiendas)

TRACKLIST

"The Collapse" - 5:14
"Order Restored" - 5:07
"All These Changes" - 4:42
"Take Control" - 3:58
"Time Erase" - 3:01
"Haunt My Mind" - 4:03
"This War Time" - 3:58
"The Credit "We" Deserve" - 4:51
"Tap Dancing In A Minefield" - 4:04
"Somethings" - 3:47

Quality: MP3 @ 112kbps ( i know it's not the best quality but if you like it and you want better quality just buy it) (we're waiting for the physical release)


The First Solo album From Ilan Rubin (The guy with the hair that play the drums 

with Nine Inch Nails


This Solo Project is Called THE NEW REGIME and the album title is COUP. Released 

November 18th 2008 via itunes, amazon mp3, etc. (looking forward for the physical 

release)


10 tracks written, played and recorded by Ilan, each note of piano, guitar, bass, 

drums is played by Ilan who also sings and makes backup vocals.

Enjoy And support THE NEW REGIME
